flowchart TD
  A[QA findings] --> B[Revision Planner]
  B --> C[Patch instructions]
  C --> D[Apply low-cost revision]
  D --> E[Create new asset version]
  E --> F[QA re-check]
  F --> G{Pass?}
  G -- Yes --> H[Advance]
  G -- No --> I{Max loops reached?}
  I -- No --> B
  I -- Yes --> J[Needs human review]
